Package: minimage
Type: Package
Title: An R Interface to the 'compress-images' Software
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Gohel", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "david.gohel@ardata.fr")
    )
Description: Minify size images with extensions: 'jpg/jpeg', 'svg', 'png' and 'gif'. 
 The main function allows to compress the images contained in a directory to another 
 directory, optionally changing some compression parameters.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: tools, locatexec
SystemRequirements: Node.js
